  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join us</h1><p>Bilibili@司马别哔哔<br>QQ Group：619757713</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/b606ef10347ff095a597bde105c30d5f.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·The leader of the alliance died, the Jianghu was in turmoil, and the undercurrent surged among various forces<br>·Each branch climbs high, each takes what he needs, and the escort sect colludes with each other<br>·One family dominates the market and bullies the people. It is a disaster to Wulin<br>·Break through the darkness, help chivalry, and reshape the glory of the escort agency in the past<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/837419f3e1bb1bebc4c69fecd7903619.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·Hundreds of escorts, thousands of martial arts<br>·A variety of combination strategies to create a unique dart team that only belongs to you<br>·Bodyguards make money and show their powers<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/8eadd938b71c4e41823ab62fb2f0032b.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·The constantly evolving dynamic Jianghu is difficult to distinguish between enemies and friends<br>·An open gun is easy to hide, but an arrow in the dark is hard to defend<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/e078afdfb6d26a0aa47d681bfc49cd63.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·If the escort is out, don't try to be fierce<br>·Pure slang, build relationships and avoid unnecessary fighting<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/6d9434b6533685c731078bdc2241761e.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·Immerse yourself in development, protect yourself and escort the world<br>·Make hegemony with martial arts, cover the sky with one hand and unify the Jianghu<br>·He is famous for his virtue and makes friends all over the world",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/b606ef10347ff095a597bde105c30d5f.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·The leader of the alliance died, the Jianghu was in turmoil, and the undercurrent surged among various forces<br>·Each branch climbs high, each takes what he needs, and the escort sect colludes with each other<br>·One family dominates the market and bullies the people. It is a disaster to Wulin<br>·Break through the darkness, help chivalry, and reshape the glory of the escort agency in the past<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/837419f3e1bb1bebc4c69fecd7903619.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·Hundreds of escorts, thousands of martial arts<br>·A variety of combination strategies to create a unique dart team that only belongs to you<br>·Bodyguards make money and show their powers<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/8eadd938b71c4e41823ab62fb2f0032b.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·The constantly evolving dynamic Jianghu is difficult to distinguish between enemies and friends<br>·An open gun is easy to hide, but an arrow in the dark is hard to defend<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/e078afdfb6d26a0aa47d681bfc49cd63.avif?t=1730419721\" width=800 height=120 /></span><br>·If the escort is out, don't try to be fierce<br>·Pure slang, build relationships and avoid unnecessary fighting<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700630/extras/6d9434b6533685c731078bdc2241761e.avif?t=173